803
01:01:09,615 --> 01:01:12,709
I'm sorry. It was a joke.

804
01:01:16,355 --> 01:01:18,448
I mean, be honest...

805
01:01:18,624 --> 01:01:23,118
...she didn't exactly marry me for love,
did she?

806
01:01:30,636 --> 01:01:32,763
My mother...

807
01:01:32,938 --> 01:01:38,103
...was a 24-year-old blackjack dealer
from Nebraska.

808
01:01:38,944 --> 01:01:43,176
You had to tip her $500
just to have a drink with you.

809
01:01:43,348 --> 01:01:46,875
You got married two weeks later
at the age of 175.

810
01:01:47,052 --> 01:01:48,747
- 51 to be precise.
- Now you're mad...

811
01:01:48,921 --> 01:01:52,152
...because she had the brains to get
some money before you dumped her?

812
01:01:52,324 --> 01:01:53,757
No, I'm mad about the amount.

813
01:01:53,926 --> 01:01:57,418
Oh, well, okay, you can have mine.
Because I'm cutting myself off.

814
01:01:57,596 --> 01:02:00,827
