954
01:13:33,591 --> 01:13:34,683
Fine, make it 10.

955
01:13:35,259 --> 01:13:36,726
You don't have $ 10.

956
01:13:37,495 --> 01:13:39,554
Fine, make it a million.

957
01:13:45,803 --> 01:13:47,361
What are you doing?

958
01:13:47,538 --> 01:13:50,371
