- You mean there's two?

964
01:15:19,163 --> 01:15:20,653
- There's two cannons.
- Aah!

965
01:15:20,832 --> 01:15:23,699
- And I owe you a million dollars. Aah!
- Yes, you do. Oh!

966
01:15:23,868 --> 01:15:25,301
Whoo!

967
01:15:25,737 --> 01:15:27,568
<i>We got the Aurelia, baby!</i>

968
01:15:27,739 --> 01:15:32,233
Listen to me, if anybody finds out about
this outside of our crew, we are screwed.

969
01:15:32,410 --> 01:15:35,004
Wow. Can't you just enjoy this
for a second?

970
01:15:36,247 --> 01:15:38,272
Oh, I'm enjoying it.

971
01:15:42,153 --> 01:15:45,316
Oh, God. Thank God.

972
01:15:48,960 --> 01:15:51,394
Whoo-hoo!

973
01:16:18,623 --> 01:16:19,920
Well, there's not much here.

974
01:16:20,091 --> 01:16:24,027
Now, they probably burned the ship
and took everything inland.

975
01:16:24,195 --> 01:16:27,653
Look, a pistol.
Cool.

976
01:16:27,832 --> 01:16:31,165
All right, well, what do we know
about Topsail Cay?

977
01:16:31,569 --> 01:16:33,901
We got the town, the church...

978
01:16:34,071 --> 01:16:35,197
There's Preacher's Cave.

979
01:16:35,373 --> 01:16:38,399
We were up there once.
It said something about first settlers...

980
01:16:38,576 --> 01:16:39,600
...religious freedom...

981
01:16:39,777 --> 01:16:42,302
God, I think that is just so important.

982
01:16:44,015 --> 01:16:45,312
Yeah, but that was like...

983
01:16:46,217 --> 01:16:49,709
- Oh.
- Like 1780-something.

984
01:16:50,855 --> 01:16:54,120
I mean, Sebastian beat them here
by almost 70 years.

985
01:16:54,292 --> 01:16:56,487
If there are any records,
they're in the church.

986
01:16:56,661 --> 01:16:59,892
- Letters, journals, sermons.
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

987
01:17:01,232 --> 01:17:03,359
That's smart, Tess.

